content.description: Start on same holds as Julie but go right. Grab sloper dish with right hand and trough sloper above (left hand on) go for pinch (right hand). Dino for jug on lip above. Left heel helps.
content.location: Its the line right next to Juliet. On Road Side bolder. Its overhang on back side.

content.description: Jump start on large jug. Go right to join Dominator. Use some edgis and tricky foot work. Its bit scary bat good problem.
content.location: Its link up to Dominator from left side. All problems located on Road Side Bolder. (either you can see from road)

content.description: Start on moon kind futures. And campus up. Right heel helps. At the top scary but its all there.
content.protection: 1-2 pad this problem can be used as way down from other problems on same bolder so watch for a traffic.....
content.location: About 100 feet from Road Side Bolder right (if you stand on the road). Or just follow road. You can see problem from there. Its quite big bolder named Bullet Shots (has two bullet hols from site).

content.description: Sit start on big jug down and left. Climb straight up. Finish mantel on lip above.
content.location: Problem is located on back site of bolder. Its closest block from road.

content.description: Its depend how you start. You can use crimp for right hand end left big slopi edge. Or just match on edge/corner (its harder). Follow the corner up.
content.protection: 1-2 pad use Moon Walk as down climb
content.location: Its on the other side of Bullet Shoots bolder. Problem follows arete.

content.description: Start match hands over on slopy almost crimp. Go straight up a little right and up again. This problem its super good little technical. Have fun.
content.protection: 2 pads safely!!!! Problem its right against to road!!!! Beware of any problems. Watch for traffic!!
content.location: The problem its on same bolder as Romeo and Julie only from other site (right from road). You can park from right on site of bolder. And walk round to other problems from there.
